n today's claims than to face a backlog that feels like it would take weeks. So it keeps growing until someone separates it into a prioritized, workable recovery plan."}]]}]]}]]}]]}]}],"$undefined",["$","section",null,{"className":"block block--ink","id":"solution","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"block-head fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"The recovery solution"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"display display--light","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"The recovery solution"}}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We turn your aging AR backlog into a prioritized recovery plan. Then we execute it."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"two-col fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-list","children":[["$","div","01",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"01"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"Complete aging AR audit"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"A full review of your outstanding AR — every claim categorized by age, payer, value, and last activity. The foundation of a recovery plan that is actually workable, not just a list of old balances."}]]}]]}],["$","div","02",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"02"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"Collectibility assessment claim by claim"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"High-value claims get individual review. Volume buckets get categorical assessment. Output is a prioritized recovery list — each claim categorized as high-priority, standard follow-up, escalation needed, or write-off review required."}]]}]]}],["$","div","03",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"03"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"Recovery sequenced by return potential"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"High-value, high-probability claims worked first. Early cash recovery makes the overall effort visible and valuable quickly — instead of spending weeks on low-probability accounts with marginal returns."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"process-list","children":[["$","div","04",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"04"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"Each claim worked through the right recovery channel"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Payer portal follow-up, phone calls, corrected resubmission, appeal filing, timely filing exceptions, coordination of benefits resolution — each claim gets the approach its specific situation requires."}]]}]]}],["$","div","05",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"05"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"Write-offs reviewed and documented"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"No claim written off without a documented collectibility review and a real attempt at recovery. Every write-off applied with a specific reason — not based on age alone."}]]}]]}],["$","div","06",{"className":"process-item","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"process-num","children":"06"}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"Prevention summary delivered at the end"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After the backlog is worked down, we deliver a documented summary of the upstream process gaps that allowed it to age — so your leadership has specific, actionable information to prevent the same pattern from rebuilding."}]]}]]}]]}]]}]]}]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"block","id":"services","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"block-head fade-in","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"eyebrow","children":"Recovery services"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"display","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"From audit to recovery. <em>Every step managed.